data.description: Incredible renovation from Watchtower Homes & Construction in RVA’s South Side neighborhood! Just minutes away from The James River, Hatch Local, The Continental Manchester, Legends Brewery, and many other restaurants and entertainment Manchester has to offer. After being taken down to the studs, there’s new plumbing, electrical, HVAC, and roof. Inside you’ll find an open layout with attention to detail and craftsmanship at every turn. 9ft+ Ceiling, hardwood floors throughout, recessed lighting, ceiling fans, gorgeous eat-in kitchen featuring shaker cabinets w/ soft close/dovetail features, granite counters, SS appliances, and ample bar seating. Along the right side of the house are two good-sized bedrooms, one equipped with its own on-suite tub/shower combo. Off the rear of the house is a nice sized mud room/ laundry room, and second full bath. Additional features are a large fully fenced yard and off-street parking. Schedule your appointments today!
